                <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/9fQSDnc72u7CE4P69" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">LG Silicon Valley Lab</a>
              </p>
            </div>
            <a href="https://lu.ma/kpai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary text-sm !py-2 !px-4">
